        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A daily two-minute ritual for meeting money from a steadier place before the day starts. Not a full ceremony. Not a deep practice. A short daily habit that, done consistently, shifts the baseline.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to rituals? Read ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "how rituals work",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "/mindset/how-rituals-work"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " first.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The practice",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Step 1: One breath",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Sit upright. Take one slow breath in through your nose, hold for a count of three, and let it out through your mouth. Feel your feet on the floor.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Step 2: One statement",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Say one of the following aloud, hand on chest. Pick the one that fits today, or rotate through them across the week:",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "pullQuote",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "Money is not a threat. It is a resource I am learning to work with.",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "pullQuote",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "Today I meet money with steadiness rather than fear.",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "pullQuote",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "I am building a different relationship with money, one day at a time.",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Step 3: One intention",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Name one money-adjacent thing you will do today from a place of steadiness rather than anxiety. It does not have to be large. Open the app. Transfer the ten pounds. Reply to the email.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
